<i>adverb</i>: 영영 [영ː영], 영구히 [영ː구히], 길이 [기리] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영영 [영ː영]</dt><br>
<dd>forever; permanently; eternally</dd><br>
<dd>영원히 언제까지나.</dd><br>
<dd>For ever and ever.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영구히 [영ː구히]</dt><br>
<dd>permanently</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 오래 지나도 변하지 않고 무한히 계속되는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of lasting endlessly without changing with time.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>길이 [기리]</dt><br>
<dd>forever; permanently</dd><br>
<dd>오랫동안 계속해서 내내.</dd><br>
<dd>Abidingly for a long time.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>